➜广东诗人小隐：破阵子．山村雨景
http://www.sohu.com/a/416646328_100115135	47162
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200905/712eb63c8e7f4fed9db40d26d4861bba.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>破阵子．山村雨景</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/小隐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">昨夜秋风生梦，今朝竹影摇窗。趁露水浓花果笑，披衣朝东奔向阳。采风兴致狂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远处云山雨急，家家帘卷收箱。叩谢天公来送爽，看稻翻浪谷满仓。人间正道长。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200905/35b00220f5304fc2b35ddfd737b3428e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
