➜湖北诗人朱翠荣（清美玉洁）：白露为霜
http://www.sohu.com/a/416652897_100115135	51334
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200905/522bc2f7f7104906b09a950357cb99e2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>白露为霜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/朱翠荣(武汉)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">满笺情系我已故的亲人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寄往天堂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">回忆不尽九月的离殇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逆行着，一片青洲未染鬓霜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蒹葭苍苍在水一方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">骑着幼时梦马奔跑，在哪寻您</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总想爬上你的肩膀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">多想贴近您宽大装满欢乐的胸膛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可总是追赶不上您的匆忙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那时你的果子正在灌浆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那时你正收割事业的金黄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那时草木抽干您的血浆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那些逝水流年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>留不住东流的江水沧浪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那时白露还未凝霜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>大江南北销完了您的时光</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
